<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>登录验证码</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 10px; padding: 30px; margin-top: 20px;">
    <h2 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 20px;">登录验证码</h2>
    <p>您好，</p>
    <p>您正在尝试登录，验证码如下：</p>
    <div style="background: #fff; border: 2px dashed #3498db; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
      <span style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #3498db;">{{code}}</span>
    </div>
    <p style="color: #e74c3c; font-size: 14px;">验证码有效期为 {{expiresIn}}，请尽快使用。</p>
    <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 30px;">如果您没有进行此操作，请忽略此邮件。</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
